width2: alt=Logo reading "Nupedia.com the free encyclopedia" in blue with the large initial "N"|Wikipedia originally developed from another encyclopedia project called Nupedia. Various collaborative online encyclopedias were attempted before the start of Wikipedia, but with limited success.   Wikipedia began as a complementary project for Nupedia, a free online English-language encyclopedia project whose articles were written by experts and reviewed under a formal process.
